-- Ford shares rise after results
-- 
-- Mon Nov 2, 2009 7:09am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/11/02/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-ford-idUSTRE5A11YE20091102

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Ford Motor Co rose 5 percent to $7.35 in premarket trading on Monday, after the company reported its quarterly results. 

 (Reporting by  Ryan Vlastelica )